<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA52">
<l>aṅkaṇ muḻumatiyañ cekka rakalvāṉat</l>
<l>teṅku miṉiteḻuntā lovvātē - ceṅkaṇ</l>
<l>ṭirumālaip paṅkuṭaiyāṉ ceñcaṭaimēl vaitta</l>
<l>ciramālai tōṉṟuvatōr cīr</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the pretty-eyed/spotted full moon rises everywhere sweetly</l>
<l>in the wide red sky, it is not equal to the excellence</l>
<l>that appears in the skull garland which is put on the red matted hair</l>
<l>of him who has on one side red-eyed Tirumāl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
